"seamlessly integrates with GNOME. Podcasts can play various audio formats "
"and remember where you stopped listening. You can subscribe to shows via "
"RSS/Atom, iTunes, and Soundcloud links. Subscriptions from other apps can be"
" imported via OPML files."
